19#include "ODRSSDataCharacter.h"
20#include "ODRSSFinderPattern.h"
21
22namespace ZXing {
23namespace OneD {
24namespace RSS {
25
26class Pair : public DataCharacter
27{
28 FinderPattern _finderPattern;
29 int _count = 0;
30
31public:
32 Pair() = default;
33 Pair(int value, int checksumPortion, const FinderPattern& finderPattern) : DataCharacter(value, checksumPortion), _finderPattern(finderPattern), _count(1) {}
34
35 const FinderPattern& finderPattern() const {
36 return _finderPattern;
37 }
38
39 int count() const {
40 return _count;
41 }
42
43 void incrementCount() {
44 _count++;
45 }
46
47 bool operator==(const Pair& other) const {
48 return DataCharacter::operator==(other) && other.finderPattern().value() == finderPattern().value();
49 }
50};
51
52} // RSS
53} // OneD
54} // ZXing
